data: Just imagine, it was Moby, so I went to say hello to him, and he told me "Would you give me a hand with my decks?" So I went, and when we finished he gave me a t-shirt and a gold pass to see the concert from the front row! Oh my God, Kim, that's the best thing that's ever happened to me! Well, Kim, I hope to receive a letter from you soon, and please tell everyone about the Moby concert and everything; thanks.
